[{"ave_id":"AVE-2009-0002","file_name":"2009/AVE-2009-0002.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2009-0545","title":"ZeroShell 1.0beta11 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"ZeroShell 1.0beta11 及更早版本的 cgi-bin/kerbynet 脚本中存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向 NoAuthREQ x509List 动作的 type 参数中注入 shell 元字符，触发任意命令执行。该漏洞影响 ZeroShell 1.0beta11 及之前版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。目前官方尚未发布补丁，建议限制相关页面的网络访问。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2009-0545"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2009-02-12T23:30:01.170","updated":"2026-06-16T23:05:16.320","remediation":"升级至 ZeroShell 1.0beta12 或更高版本；若无法升级，对 1.0beta11 应用官方补丁 C100（zeroshell.net/eng/patch-details/#C100）；临时缓解措施：在防火墙或反向代理层限制对 /cgi-bin/kerbynet 的未授权访问，并对 web 管理控制台启用 IP 白名单或 HTTP 认证。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ikkisoft.com/stuff/LC-2009-01.txt","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/500763/100/0/threaded","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2009/0385","http://www.zeroshell.net/eng/announcements/","http://www.zeroshell.net/eng/patch-details/#C100","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/8023","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-0545.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2009/CVE-2009-0545.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/490586283f9ca1596471e5230c91d74f96495bb9/http/cves/2009/CVE-2009-0545.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/critical/cve-2009-0545-1407.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2009-0545.js","https://github.com/itsmenaga/Nuclei-Templates-All/blob/7e93c24e44969db15f4072e1c6a322a026452d6b/CVE-2009/CVE-2009-0545_%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%8D%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.yaml","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder4/cve-2009-0545-1402.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob